      "writtenOn": "2020-06-13T19:39:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I believe that we are comparing common/sync/parallel and common/sync/dispatcher here. To me, they provide similar functionalities, but I still prefer dispatcher over parallel because it supports better retry mechanism. It retries failed tasks with tunable exponential backoff and  provides a storage, b.Meta, which can be used to share data between retry attempts.",
      "parentUuid": "a4e6300f_c97e2ea7",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 50,
        "startChar": 18,
        "endLine": 50,
        "endChar": 19
      },
      "revId": "35c8bc978028972924fb2178e1b2f4e8a3f203be",
