      "writtenOn": "2020-06-13T19:50:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i was comparing dispatcher to plain old Go channel `artifactChan chan uploadArtifact`.\ndispatcher is very useful when we process batches, but here all batches are size 1 (i.e. no batching), so it defeats the purpose, it seems",
