      "writtenOn": "2020-06-13T20:28:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Even with old Go channel, we need to maintain a worker pool to maintain the concurrency level. If we implement the worker pool with an old Go channel, wouldn\u0027t it be similar to sync/parallel?\n\nWith MaxLeases\u003d4, BatchSize\u003d1, buffer.BlockNewItems{MaxItems: 2000}, there can be at most 4 active leases, each is handled by 4 different workers in parallel.",
